reviewText: Engrossing look at the important (and hardcore) work of L.A. County Coroner Investigators as they visit scenes of death to determine what happen to individuals. Very graphic but well worth watching.

As a college level criminal justice system instructor....I can't begin to describe the value of the "L.A. Coroner's Death Detectives" as an educational tool ! The informational content of this video is amazing and provides a wealth of in-sight into one of the nations largest coroners offices and the processes involved in the four modes of death investigations......;
